TODAY'S QUOTE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"The umbrella is very much linked to the greatness of kings." 
</P>
<P>
 -- Christo, the controversial artist who plans to set out 1,700 yellow, 
octagonal umbrellas, each 28 feet in diameter, on each side of Interstate 5 
from Gorman to the bottom of the Grapevine in October, 1991. 
</P>
