exhibition at Newport Harbor museum. MARIANNA DIAMOS / Los Angeles Times; 
Photo, Photograph of collage "Christo: The Umbrellas, Joint Project for Japan 
and the U.S.A." Says the artist: "The umbrella is something extremely familiar 
to everyone around the world." Jeanne-Claude Christo 1987 
</P>
