<DATELINE>
<P>
NEWCASTLE, Australia 
</P>
</DATELINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Unbeaten Australian light-heavyweight boxer Jeff Harding pounded out a 
unanimous 10-round decision over American Art Jimmerson today to move a step 
closer to a world title fight. 
</P>
<P>
Harding, 23, upped his record to 13-0, including 11 knockouts, by dominating 
